    "summary": "The user is pressuring the assistant to provide a definitive \"yes\" regarding a drill's ability to last 24 hours under extreme conditions to facilitate a massive sale. The assistant repeatedly refuses to give a false guarantee, instead providing nuanced technical caveats and recommending more appropriate power solutions to avoid downtime.",
